# MemoryManager Class Role

The [src/ask_llm/memory.py](mdc:src/ask_llm/memory.py) file defines the `MemoryManager` class. Its responsibilities include:

*   Initializing the vector database (`ChromaDB`) client (potentially persistent).
*   Loading the `sentence-transformers` embedding model.
*   Providing methods to add messages (`add_memory`) and search for relevant past messages (`search_relevant_memories`).
*   Handling lazy loading of dependencies to improve startup time when memory is disabled.
